        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3442030841" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17372724768377419214">HOLY CRAP! THIS IS A MASTERPIECE!!<br/><br/>There&apos;s a bollywood film called &quot;Ugly&quot; and in it&apos;s trailer it says: &quot;When the going gets desperate, the desperate gets...Ugly.&quot; And that implies so perfectly here... because It does get DESPERATE and it does get UGLY.<br/><br/><br/>It&apos;s a classic tale of found treasure, greed, desperate measures and the spiral into murderous mayhem. <br/><br/>It was very intense and unnerving. Very unapologetic with the depictions of flawed human psyche. The characters so masterfully crafted and the atm</span>
  <span id="freeText17372724768377419214" style="display:none">HOLY CRAP! THIS IS A MASTERPIECE!!<br /><br />There's a bollywood film called "Ugly" and in it's trailer it says: "When the going gets desperate, the desperate gets...Ugly." And that implies so perfectly here... because It does get DESPERATE and it does get UGLY.<br /><br /><br />It's a classic tale of found treasure, greed, desperate measures and the spiral into murderous mayhem. <br /><br />It was very intense and unnerving. Very unapologetic with the depictions of flawed human psyche. The characters so masterfully crafted and the atmosphere so dreadful with the sense of an impending doom hanging in the air.<br /><br />It never got boring. It never ceased to create tension and It never ceased to amaze me. It's perfect. AND IT'S A MUST READ!</span>
  <a data-text-id="17372724768377419214" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


